# Cursor Rules

## Location
Place rules in `PROJECT_ROOT/.cursor/rules/` with `.mdc` extension.

## File Structure
```
---
description: Short description
globs: optional/path/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---
# Rule Title

Content with markdown and code examples.
```

## Naming
- Use kebab-case: `my-rule-name.mdc`
- Descriptive of rule's purpose
